Cell.Text: [S] G|Still eager to please. This is good. Skjor may be right about you. | He has something special planned for you. Better talk to him.
You wanted to see me?
[S] Yes. I have something a little different planned this time. | But it's not for everyone to hear. Meet me in the Underforge tonight. | We will speak more.
[S] Yes, I have something special for you. | But it's not for everyone to hear. Meet me in the Underforge tonight. | We will speak more.
[S] G|Skjor was looking for you before. Talk to him before doing anything else.

[S] He was one of the strongest we had, but numbers can overwhelm. He should not have come without a Shield-Brother. | Get out of here. I'm going to make sure we got the last of them, and see if there's any information to be gotten from the bodies. | You and I have work to do. The Silver Hand will tremble at our sight.

[S] There's a pack of werewolf hunters camped nearby, at Gallows Rock. | The Silver Hand. I think you've met them before. | We're going to slaughter them. All of them. | Lead on. Skjor's already scouting ahead.
That is your choice. We will not force you. But to join the Circle, your blood must be as ours. | Meet us here when you're ready.

Node.Caption: C03AelaSkjorWerewolvesBaaaaaadBranchTopic: What if I don't want to be a werewolf?

Cell.Text: The Silver Hand have taken over the old fort at Gallows Rock. They always make such easy prey.
What is this place?
Old fort. Abandoned for years. They're like jackals, making their home anywhere they can find.
Yours was not an easy transformation. But you're still alive, so congratulations. | We even have a celebration planned for you.
The bastards... somehow they managed to kill Skjor.
I forget that you've never seen it. Beneath the Skyforge, where Eorlund works. | The door is hidden, but I will show you the way.
G|Aela will be joining us shortly. Once she's inside, we can follow.
Are you prepared?

[S] G|Here's all you need to know. Jorrvaskr is the oldest building in Whiterun. The Skyforge was here long before it was. | And the Underforge taps an ancient magic that is older than men or elves. | We bring you hear to make you stronger, new blood. Now lets move.
[S] G|This is no test, new blood. This is a gift. Come inside.

Node.Caption: C03SkjorYeahWhatever: I'm ready for whatever test is next.

Cell.Text: Are you prepared to join your spirit with the beast world, friend?
[S] G|Very well.
S|You were born into the pack, brother.
S|You were born into the pack, sister.
I almost envy you. That first time is always the most... intense. | You gave us even more trouble than Farkas did at his first turning.

You have the blood of the wolf in you. You'll need to build up your strength before you can call on it again, though. | Just be careful where you do it. Some cowards in this land can't stand the sight of glory before them.
Nothing, until you choose to use it. | Then, well... you got a taste. Stronger, faster. | It doesn't last long, though. The blood of your foes can sustain you, though. If you're willing to feed.

Node.Caption: C03AelaWhatAreTheRulesTopic: What does it mean to be a werewolf?

Cell.Text: Cure? Hah. You're sounding like the old man. | I... shouldn't say that. | I love Kodlak. I respect and follow him. But he's wrong on this. It's no curse. We're made into the greatest hunters in the land. | If he's worried about some mead-swilling afterlife in Sovngarde, he's free to pursue it. I'll take the glories of the hunt right here.
